WEBVTT

01:30.940 --> 01:35.030
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.780 --> 01:39.370
[2005]

01:41.229 --> 01:43.400
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

01:45.070 --> 01:45.600
Xiaolan,

01:45.759 --> 01:46.509
you rarely

01:46.509 --> 01:47.229
hang out with us.

01:47.229 --> 01:48.759
We've never heard you sing.

01:48.789 --> 01:51.310
I-I'm a terrible singer.

01:51.870 --> 01:53.000
I think I'll pass.

01:53.590 --> 01:55.390
What song would you like to hear?

02:07.250 --> 02:10.300
[Episode 20 The Most Romantic Thing]

02:12.710 --> 02:16.079
[Spring, 1991]

02:21.870 --> 02:23.070
[Mr. Chen Xiliang, Ms. Teresa Li]

02:27.190 --> 02:28.470
Congratulations.

02:30.240 --> 02:31.680
Hope you're the next one to get married.

02:31.680 --> 02:32.310
Zhenzhu,

02:32.310 --> 02:33.710
you look stunning today.

02:35.960 --> 02:37.000
Hello, uncles, aunties.

02:37.000 --> 02:38.060
Hello, Auntie Liu.

02:39.640 --> 02:40.440
Sis Bai.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.400
Do I look good?

02:41.400 --> 02:42.680
Yes, terrific.

02:42.800 --> 02:43.240
Listen,

02:43.240 --> 02:44.150
now you're a mix

02:44.480 --> 02:46.370
of heroism and charm,

02:46.400 --> 02:48.150
efficiency and gentleness.

02:48.910 --> 02:49.360
Okay.

02:49.640 --> 02:50.630
Nice compliments.

02:50.630 --> 02:51.630
I won't change my clothes to go

02:51.630 --> 02:52.410
pick up the goods later.

02:52.410 --> 02:53.400
You'll handle all the work.

02:53.400 --> 02:53.960
No problem.

02:53.960 --> 02:54.870
To help you stay pretty,

02:54.870 --> 02:56.380
I'll do my part of the job and yours.

02:56.380 --> 02:57.840
You're such a bootlicker.

02:59.600 --> 03:00.240
Auntie Liu,

03:00.240 --> 03:00.870
the wedding's about to start.

03:00.870 --> 03:02.310
Why isn't Xiaolan here yet?

03:02.310 --> 03:03.590
Xiaolan told me to come without her

03:03.590 --> 03:04.400
since she had something to do.

03:04.400 --> 03:05.730
She should arrive soon.

03:08.430 --> 03:10.960
Magpies in the sky
are chirping with delight.

03:10.960 --> 03:13.220
A couple on earth is to be wedded tonight.

03:13.400 --> 03:14.530
Everyone, thank you

03:14.560 --> 03:15.470
for attending

03:15.840 --> 03:17.079
the grand wedding ceremony

03:17.079 --> 03:19.210
for Mr. Chen Xiliang and Ms. Teresa Li.

03:19.250 --> 03:21.160
Here, on behalf of the newlyweds,

03:21.190 --> 03:22.100
I'd like to extend

03:22.100 --> 03:23.940
a warm welcome to all of you!

03:23.970 --> 03:24.840
Welcome!

03:28.390 --> 03:28.920
Now,

03:29.000 --> 03:30.800
let's give a big round

03:31.079 --> 03:32.150
of applause

03:32.150 --> 03:33.280
to this happy couple

03:33.400 --> 03:36.079
as they make their glamorous entrance!

03:54.810 --> 03:55.410
Come here!

03:55.750 --> 03:56.680
Hurry, Xiaolan.

03:57.190 --> 03:58.000
It just began.

03:58.000 --> 03:58.360
Okay.

04:07.910 --> 04:09.710
They are such a perfect match

04:09.710 --> 04:10.870
made for each other.

04:10.870 --> 04:12.030
Won't you say so?

04:12.280 --> 04:13.430
-Yes!
-Yes!

04:13.800 --> 04:15.190
The groom is such

04:15.640 --> 04:18.010
a handsome man with an elegant bearing.

04:18.040 --> 04:18.600
Guys,

04:18.870 --> 04:19.920
isn't he charming?

04:19.920 --> 04:21.120
-Yes!
-Very much so!

04:21.190 --> 04:22.160
The bride

04:22.360 --> 04:24.890
is breathtakingly beautiful.

04:24.920 --> 04:25.650
Guys,

04:25.680 --> 04:26.800
isn't she pretty?

04:26.830 --> 04:28.240
-Yes!
-So pretty!

04:28.310 --> 04:28.800
Next,

04:28.950 --> 04:30.270
let's move on to the first part

04:30.270 --> 04:30.950
of the wedding.

04:30.950 --> 04:32.110
What took you two so long?

04:32.110 --> 04:33.950
We were preparing a gift for Chen Xiliang.

04:33.950 --> 04:35.000
It cost us some time.

04:35.000 --> 04:35.720
What gift?

04:36.930 --> 04:37.730
It's a secret.

04:43.390 --> 04:45.120
-Bite it!
-Go for it!

04:49.720 --> 04:51.000
-Try again!
-Once again!

04:51.000 --> 04:52.600
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

04:55.159 --> 04:55.820
Do it again!

05:00.110 --> 05:00.910
Is it done now?

05:01.510 --> 05:02.070
All done!

05:02.560 --> 05:02.960
Bravo!

05:03.800 --> 05:05.120
Come on, Sis Bai, Auntie Liu.

05:05.120 --> 05:06.000
H-Have some pork.

05:06.000 --> 05:07.830
Auntie Liu, try the roast suckling pig.

05:07.830 --> 05:09.030
Get me some more meat.

05:09.750 --> 05:11.390
We'd like to raise a toast to you all.

05:11.390 --> 05:12.720
Here is the bride and groom.

05:12.720 --> 05:14.070
Congrats on your wedding!

05:14.070 --> 05:14.630
Congrats!

05:14.630 --> 05:16.290
Thanks. Thank you, everyone.

05:21.950 --> 05:22.430
Xia.

05:23.310 --> 05:24.110
This toast...

05:25.120 --> 05:26.320
is especially to you.

05:26.390 --> 05:27.050
Without you

05:27.070 --> 05:27.680
or Luna,

05:27.950 --> 05:28.630
Teresa and I

05:28.630 --> 05:30.430
wouldn't have gotten together.

05:30.870 --> 05:31.480
Xiaolan,

05:31.680 --> 05:32.510
thank you for recommending

05:32.510 --> 05:33.950
I shoot the commercial back then.

05:33.950 --> 05:35.350
I'm very grateful to you.

05:35.630 --> 05:36.680
Chen, Teresa,

05:36.950 --> 05:37.950
even without me,

05:37.970 --> 05:39.040
Luna would've been established

05:39.040 --> 05:40.680
and you would've become a happy couple
as you are today.

05:40.680 --> 05:42.190
You created all that yourselves.

05:42.190 --> 05:42.650
Cheers.

05:42.950 --> 05:43.409
Cheers.

05:43.560 --> 05:44.480
Thanks to you all.

05:44.480 --> 05:45.540
Congratulations!

05:45.560 --> 05:46.690
Thank you so much...

05:47.050 --> 05:48.159
for taking time out to be with us.

05:48.159 --> 05:48.920
Many thanks.

05:49.190 --> 05:49.870
Goodbye.

05:49.870 --> 05:50.600
Take care.

05:51.120 --> 05:52.450
I won't see you off then!

05:53.120 --> 05:53.720
Chen.

05:55.390 --> 05:56.520
You're leaving too?

05:56.800 --> 05:57.600
No, we're not.

05:58.720 --> 05:59.980
A wedding gift for you.

06:02.160 --> 06:03.000
Car keys?

06:03.680 --> 06:04.610
What do you mean?

06:05.120 --> 06:06.750
The car is not just for you,

06:06.750 --> 06:07.880
but for Luna as well.

06:08.000 --> 06:09.240
You'll need a car for meeting clients

06:09.240 --> 06:09.830
and whatever

06:09.830 --> 06:11.230
in the future, won't you?

06:12.070 --> 06:13.600
This is too big a gift.

06:13.600 --> 06:14.560
I can't take it.

06:14.630 --> 06:15.360
Just keep it.

06:15.480 --> 06:15.990
It's fine.

06:15.990 --> 06:17.320
There's one more thing.

06:18.580 --> 06:19.870
Please read the agreement.

06:19.870 --> 06:21.750
I'm afraid Xiaolan will be too busy
to involve herself

06:21.750 --> 06:23.310
in Luna's business from now on.

06:23.310 --> 06:23.950
So...

06:24.950 --> 06:27.370
[Equity Transfer Agreement]

06:31.820 --> 06:39.790
♪ The stars flow across the sky,
and I walk this road with you ♪

06:32.870 --> 06:33.480
Xia,

06:34.040 --> 06:35.040
Luna was built up

06:35.040 --> 06:35.900
by us together.

06:35.950 --> 06:37.070
Why don't we sit down and talk about

06:37.070 --> 06:37.930
this decision?

06:38.040 --> 06:38.970
-I think…
-Chen,

06:39.270 --> 06:40.360
didn't we already make a pact

06:40.360 --> 06:41.510
in the very beginning?

06:40.600 --> 06:44.540
♪ From strangers,
our hearts slowly grow close ♪

06:44.680 --> 06:48.060
♪ Quietly, we treat each other
with sincerity ♪

06:45.159 --> 06:45.820
Yes, we did.

06:46.310 --> 06:47.570
You said from the start

06:47.920 --> 06:49.560
that selling clothes wasn't your dream.

06:49.030 --> 06:56.950
♪ Life is like a dream,
and friends are like a mist ♪

06:52.310 --> 06:53.170
How about this?

06:53.630 --> 06:54.230
If you ever

06:54.390 --> 06:55.800
need my help in the future,

06:55.800 --> 06:56.730
just let me know.

06:57.040 --> 06:58.159
Don't stand on ceremony at all.

06:58.100 --> 07:01.890
♪ True confidants are rare,
after storms and trials ♪

06:58.800 --> 06:59.730
I, Chen Xiliang,

06:59.800 --> 07:01.000
might not have great capability,

07:01.000 --> 07:01.860
but I'll always

07:02.100 --> 07:09.010
♪ The one who never steps back for me,
that is you ♪

07:02.190 --> 07:03.790
do whatever I can to help you.

07:05.480 --> 07:08.140
When your residential buildings
are finished,

07:08.270 --> 07:09.750
I'll definitely buy an apartment.

07:09.750 --> 07:13.680
♪ In the distant night sky,
the scattered stars are all connected ♪

07:10.190 --> 07:10.600
Okay.

07:11.240 --> 07:12.750
Congrats on the wedding, Chen.

07:12.750 --> 07:13.350
Thank you.

07:13.710 --> 07:19.210
♪ Even if the road ahead
is full of thorns ♪

07:14.720 --> 07:15.360
Xiliang!

07:16.750 --> 07:17.360
Coming!

07:17.830 --> 07:18.680
I need to go now.

07:18.680 --> 07:19.070
Sure.

07:19.240 --> 07:19.770
Go ahead.

07:20.050 --> 07:23.180
♪ You help untangle
the loneliness in my heart ♪

07:20.360 --> 07:21.220
I'll keep this.

07:22.750 --> 07:23.210
Here I come!

07:23.210 --> 07:26.770
♪ Who truly understands me? ♪

07:27.170 --> 07:31.080
♪ Like two hands,
together in joy and in sorrow ♪

07:31.110 --> 07:36.790
♪ We share everything,
never dividing between you and me ♪

07:37.580 --> 07:41.710
♪ You for me, and I for you ♪

07:41.270 --> 07:42.470
What's wrong, honey?

07:42.530 --> 07:48.680
♪ Facing hardship and despair together,
tightly holding your hand ♪

07:47.950 --> 07:48.409
Listen,

07:49.159 --> 07:50.360
you don't want to waste your time on them.

07:50.360 --> 07:50.920
Let's go.

07:51.720 --> 07:52.320
Pardon me.

07:52.870 --> 07:54.730
You don't sound like a gentleman.

07:55.159 --> 07:57.750
It looks like this lady
has something to say.

07:59.000 --> 07:59.430
Okay.

08:00.190 --> 08:00.800
Then you guys talk.

08:00.800 --> 08:02.330
I'll wait for you upstairs.

08:05.070 --> 08:05.600
What now?

08:06.240 --> 08:07.800
Are you here to laugh at me?

08:09.510 --> 08:10.040
Ji Ya,

08:10.240 --> 08:11.240
don't you think you're a bit

08:11.240 --> 08:12.390
too full of yourself?

08:12.390 --> 08:14.510
I don't know what you're talking about.

08:14.510 --> 08:15.360
Xia, Zhou Cheng!

08:15.360 --> 08:16.510
I knew you would still be around.

08:16.510 --> 08:17.720
I just ran into
some garment factory staff.

08:17.720 --> 08:19.320
They told me Ji Ya's brand...

08:23.000 --> 08:24.240
Because its rapid expansion outpaced

08:24.240 --> 08:25.000
sales growth,

08:25.000 --> 08:26.190
its American investor
wouldn't inject more capital.

08:26.190 --> 08:28.050
The brand has been auctioned off.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.510
You're here too?

08:30.510 --> 08:31.390
Hello, Ms. Ji.

08:31.560 --> 08:32.549
Goodbye, Ms. Ji.

08:34.200 --> 08:34.799
Oh, right!

08:35.030 --> 08:35.730
Come have a drink

08:35.730 --> 08:36.860
on the second floor.

08:40.600 --> 08:41.330
Xia Xiaolan,

08:41.600 --> 08:43.130
you've gone way out of line.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.090
To be honest,

08:44.720 --> 08:45.510
I'm very pleased

08:45.510 --> 08:46.630
to hear about the failure

08:46.630 --> 08:48.550
of a rival of mine
who once tried to destroy me

08:48.550 --> 08:49.680
with devious means.

08:50.120 --> 08:50.790
That said,

08:51.000 --> 08:52.460
I also feel sorry about it.

08:52.910 --> 08:53.390
Ji Ya,

08:53.910 --> 08:54.480
you are

08:54.480 --> 08:55.880
an excellent designer.

08:56.260 --> 08:56.790
Elegance

08:56.840 --> 08:58.770
could have developed much better.

08:59.790 --> 09:00.960
Elegance's positioning

09:00.960 --> 09:03.320
was actually much higher-end than Luna's.

09:03.320 --> 09:04.200
In fact, we didn't have to

09:04.200 --> 09:05.870
go for a cut-throat competition.

09:05.870 --> 09:07.790
But you got willy-nilly with your actions,

09:07.790 --> 09:08.600
since you arrogantly

09:08.600 --> 09:09.960
thought there would always be

09:09.960 --> 09:11.290
someone to bail you out.

09:11.950 --> 09:12.760
Ms. Ji,

09:13.440 --> 09:15.120
the world isn't that simple.

09:15.600 --> 09:16.270
Is that so?

09:17.470 --> 09:18.870
Thank you for the advice.

09:25.620 --> 09:27.440
Ji Ya doesn't seem to care

09:27.440 --> 09:28.720
a lot about her brand.

09:30.150 --> 09:31.510
Although I did foresee

09:31.510 --> 09:33.000
that Ji Ya's reckless expansion

09:33.000 --> 09:34.330
would lead to problems,

09:34.360 --> 09:35.150
I didn't expect

09:35.150 --> 09:36.810
her brand to collapse so soon.

09:37.910 --> 09:39.000
From what Chen said,

09:39.000 --> 09:39.750
it was that American man

09:39.750 --> 09:41.480
who refused to pour more money into it.

09:41.480 --> 09:42.030
He initially

09:42.030 --> 09:44.360
invested in the brand
just to pursue Ji Ya.

09:44.630 --> 09:45.960
He is a businessman after all.

09:45.960 --> 09:47.240
He wouldn't keep throwing money

09:47.240 --> 09:48.500
into a bottomless pit.

09:48.910 --> 09:50.710
They've gone for afternoon tea.

09:50.840 --> 09:52.500
Do you think they'll enjoy it?

09:52.600 --> 09:55.030
I hope he's a faithful romantic partner.

09:55.360 --> 09:56.750
Otherwise, Ms. Ji Ya

09:56.750 --> 09:58.350
might stir up trouble again.

10:05.670 --> 10:07.200
This is my lucky place.

10:07.200 --> 10:07.910
I'm especially happy

10:07.910 --> 10:09.040
every time I am here.

10:13.390 --> 10:13.920
Xiaolan!

10:14.360 --> 10:14.760
Uncle.

10:14.840 --> 10:15.360
Ms. Xia.

10:16.070 --> 10:16.530
Come on.

10:17.150 --> 10:18.480
Quickly,

10:19.510 --> 10:21.000
tell us

10:21.030 --> 10:22.570
about the hotel.

10:22.840 --> 10:25.080
Haihua Hotel is the first
five-star international hotel

10:25.080 --> 10:26.270
in Shengcheng.

10:26.870 --> 10:27.870
Its shareholders are

10:27.870 --> 10:29.600
Meihua, Huifeng Bank,

10:29.630 --> 10:30.630
the Merchants Group,

10:30.630 --> 10:31.960
and Dongfeng Holdings.

10:32.110 --> 10:33.550
They are all from Gangdao,

10:33.550 --> 10:35.150
except Dongfeng,
the only mainland enterprise.

10:35.150 --> 10:35.600
Yes.

10:36.360 --> 10:37.750
Meihua and Dongfeng Holdings

10:37.750 --> 10:39.870
are competing
for the hotel's management rights.

10:39.870 --> 10:40.930
Meihua's proposal

10:41.030 --> 10:42.360
was vetoed by Dongfeng,

10:42.510 --> 10:43.840
while Dongfeng's plan

10:44.160 --> 10:45.470
was disproved by the three shareholders

10:45.470 --> 10:46.270
from Gangdao.

10:46.390 --> 10:47.510
So, now, Dongfeng is looking

10:47.510 --> 10:48.740
to revise their proposal,

10:48.740 --> 10:50.510
which gives us Yuanhui an opportunity.

10:50.510 --> 10:51.320
That is to say,

10:51.630 --> 10:54.120
it's not only a competition on designs,

10:54.510 --> 10:56.170
but also a battle for control.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.440
An executive of Dongfeng

10:59.440 --> 11:00.440
is in Shengcheng.

11:00.600 --> 11:01.660
His surname is Huo.

11:01.670 --> 11:03.530
He is the one we are meeting today.

11:03.720 --> 11:05.750
Yuanhui isn't the only company
eager for cooperation.

11:05.750 --> 11:06.910
There's a fierce competition,

11:06.910 --> 11:08.360
but also a good chance to shine.

11:08.360 --> 11:09.240
Today, let's first figure out

11:09.240 --> 11:10.510
what they want exactly.

11:10.510 --> 11:11.360
Okay, got it.

11:11.440 --> 11:11.960
Let's go.

11:11.960 --> 11:12.320
Go.

11:19.000 --> 11:20.270
We will follow this lead

11:20.270 --> 11:21.070
to dig deeper.

11:21.390 --> 11:22.320
As far as we know,

11:22.480 --> 11:23.960
the crane operators
on the construction site

11:23.960 --> 11:25.000
are loosely managed

11:25.000 --> 11:26.460
and replaced frequently.

11:26.670 --> 11:28.240
It's hard to find a particular someone.

11:28.240 --> 11:29.170
But don't worry.

11:29.320 --> 11:30.080
We will make sure

11:30.080 --> 11:31.080
you get an answer.

11:31.960 --> 11:32.390
I know.

11:33.080 --> 11:33.550
I won't give up

11:33.550 --> 11:34.680
on this case either.

11:34.840 --> 11:35.790
We'll keep you posted

11:35.790 --> 11:36.790
on any new developments.

11:36.790 --> 11:37.200
Okay.

11:38.150 --> 11:40.150
It's actually fine for us
to notify your law firm

11:40.150 --> 11:41.480
when anything comes up.

11:41.960 --> 11:43.480
It must be tough being attorneys like you.

11:43.480 --> 11:44.870
You shouldn't keep running back and forth.

11:44.870 --> 11:45.470
It's okay.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.120
Officer Chen.

11:49.130 --> 11:49.840
Ms. Jiang,

11:50.030 --> 11:51.560
what brings you here again?

11:51.750 --> 11:52.960
I won't give up

11:53.270 --> 11:54.670
until the case is solved.

11:55.900 --> 11:56.910
If there's nothing else,

11:56.910 --> 11:57.440
I'll be leaving then.

11:57.440 --> 11:57.790
Okay.

11:57.960 --> 11:58.560
Thank you.

12:02.720 --> 12:03.320
Jiang Yan?

12:03.550 --> 12:04.270
Zhou Cheng?

12:09.200 --> 12:10.260
You've graduated?

12:11.030 --> 12:13.670
Yes, I'm working
in the prosecution office now.

12:13.670 --> 12:15.270
You went to college in Hushi.

12:15.270 --> 12:17.510
Why did you come to Shengcheng
after graduation?

12:17.510 --> 12:18.320
What about you?

12:18.320 --> 12:19.600
Why are you in Shengcheng?

12:19.600 --> 12:20.730
Because of Xiaolan.

12:27.390 --> 12:28.250
Mr. Huo, right?

12:28.440 --> 12:29.200
Hello.

12:29.480 --> 12:31.080
I'm Liu Yong from Yuanhui.

12:31.510 --> 12:32.440
Nice to meet you.

12:32.550 --> 12:33.610
Please have a seat.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.080
Okay.

12:34.670 --> 12:35.200
Thanks.

12:41.270 --> 12:42.730
I'll cut to the chase then.

12:43.030 --> 12:44.790
Actually, someone's already working

12:44.790 --> 12:46.390
on the Haihua Hotel project.

12:46.790 --> 12:47.750
But when I heard

12:48.440 --> 12:50.000
that the designs of this guesthouse

12:50.000 --> 12:51.460
were proposed by Yuanhui,

12:52.480 --> 12:54.080
I was pleasantly surprised.

12:54.120 --> 12:55.580
It was really unexpected.

12:56.550 --> 12:58.280
Yuanhui isn't a big operation.

12:58.840 --> 13:00.700
Before this guesthouse project,

13:00.910 --> 13:02.040
it mainly focused on

13:02.390 --> 13:03.920
home interior decoration.

13:04.790 --> 13:05.870
That said, I really like

13:05.870 --> 13:07.930
the overall style of the guesthouse.

13:08.200 --> 13:08.670
If...

13:09.200 --> 13:10.600
I mean, hypothetically,

13:10.720 --> 13:11.670
if your designs

13:12.240 --> 13:13.390
are adopted

13:14.080 --> 13:16.150
for the Haihua Hotel project,

13:16.630 --> 13:17.290
I'll gladly

13:18.360 --> 13:20.690
spare one-quarter of the renovation work

13:21.030 --> 13:21.720
for you.

13:27.870 --> 13:29.400
You must be Ms. Xia Xiaolan.

13:30.270 --> 13:30.910
Ms. Xia,

13:31.360 --> 13:32.560
are you satisfied...

13:32.630 --> 13:33.490
with this plan?

13:33.670 --> 13:34.200
Mr. Huo,

13:34.510 --> 13:35.910
you're probably mistaken.

13:35.910 --> 13:37.720
Yuanhui is in the charge of my uncle.

13:37.720 --> 13:39.080
The gentleman sitting next to me

13:39.080 --> 13:39.750
is Gong Yang,

13:39.750 --> 13:41.010
a designer at Yuanhui.

13:41.440 --> 13:43.570
I might participate in the revisions,

13:43.600 --> 13:45.030
but you'll have to talk to my uncle

13:45.030 --> 13:47.160
about the details of the cooperation.

13:47.600 --> 13:49.320
Mr. Huo, you're offering Yuanhui

13:49.320 --> 13:50.550
one quarter of the Haihua Hotel

13:50.550 --> 13:51.550
renovation work.

13:51.630 --> 13:53.630
I truly appreciate your sincerity.

13:54.000 --> 13:54.510
For us, this is

13:54.510 --> 13:56.240
a great learning opportunity.

13:56.440 --> 13:57.600
I'm wondering

13:57.630 --> 13:58.750
if you can show us

13:58.750 --> 14:00.010
the previous designs.

14:01.120 --> 14:01.720
Of course.

14:32.960 --> 14:33.420
Mr. Huo,

14:34.000 --> 14:35.270
we can modify the designs,

14:35.270 --> 14:36.960
but we need some time

14:37.200 --> 14:38.360
and your support.

14:39.670 --> 14:40.910
To be honest,

14:41.120 --> 14:41.910
these designs

14:41.910 --> 14:43.480
are already perfect.

14:43.900 --> 14:45.630
If the hotel is renovated
following this plan,

14:45.630 --> 14:46.700
I'm sure it will meet

14:46.700 --> 14:48.700
the standards of a five-star hotel.

14:49.030 --> 14:49.990
May I ask

14:50.080 --> 14:51.810
who came up with these designs?

14:53.440 --> 14:55.200
Ms. Xia, you do have a good eye.

14:56.120 --> 14:57.350
Actually, these designs

14:57.350 --> 14:59.150
don't need to be modified at all,

14:59.720 --> 15:01.120
since they pair well

15:01.120 --> 15:03.380
with the main buildings of Haihua Hotel.

15:03.480 --> 15:05.120
Ms. Xia, you studied architecture.

15:05.120 --> 15:05.960
I bet

15:06.360 --> 15:08.490
you have heard about Mr. Mao Kangshan.

15:09.600 --> 15:10.060
This...

15:11.080 --> 15:12.150
is a work by Mr. Mao.

15:12.960 --> 15:14.600
Mr. Mao really is a master.

15:14.720 --> 15:16.120
Such brilliant designs.

15:16.200 --> 15:18.060
Ahead in aesthetic taste as well.

15:19.480 --> 15:20.240
How odd.

15:20.240 --> 15:21.550
Why would anyone want to modify

15:21.550 --> 15:23.010
a master's work like this?

15:23.600 --> 15:24.440
Essentially,

15:24.510 --> 15:26.550
it's not an issue
with the design proposal.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.440
It's a struggle for the rights

15:27.440 --> 15:28.550
to manage the hotel.

15:28.550 --> 15:30.480
Dongfeng Holdings doesn't have
the upper hand now.

15:30.480 --> 15:32.630
But this is Master Mao's work.

15:33.000 --> 15:34.330
If Yuanhui modifies it,

15:34.390 --> 15:35.750
its reputation in the architecture circle

15:35.750 --> 15:37.210
will be damaged, won't it?

15:38.030 --> 15:38.720
Yes.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.870
Mr. Mao is reputed
as the architectural leader

15:39.870 --> 15:41.630
in the south, and Mr. Ning the north.

15:41.630 --> 15:42.320
By Mr. Ning,

15:42.320 --> 15:43.550
I mean Mr. Mao's counterpart,

15:43.550 --> 15:44.360
Ning Yanfan.

15:44.910 --> 15:45.750
At first, they were

15:45.750 --> 15:47.550
on equal footing in the field.

15:47.790 --> 15:48.920
But in recent years,

15:49.030 --> 15:50.360
Mr. Ning has gained much prestige

15:50.360 --> 15:52.320
both internationally and domestically.

15:52.320 --> 15:53.600
Meanwhile, Mr. Mao Kangshan

15:53.600 --> 15:55.150
is known as a reclusive master

15:55.150 --> 15:57.030
by Hangcheng design institutes.

15:57.630 --> 15:58.080
Uncle,

15:58.360 --> 15:59.510
do you know why?

16:00.390 --> 16:02.320
Because Mr. Mao is indifferent to fame?

16:02.320 --> 16:04.150
That's because
Mr. Mao has a stranger temper

16:04.150 --> 16:05.210
and is quite moody.

16:05.320 --> 16:07.240
He's getting more and more
self-centered, too.

16:07.240 --> 16:09.150
I heard that he doesn't take
apprentices anymore.

16:09.150 --> 16:09.840
He does most of the work

16:09.840 --> 16:10.630
on his own.

16:11.270 --> 16:12.630
I guess he must've poured

16:12.630 --> 16:13.600
his heart and soul

16:13.600 --> 16:15.330
into the Haihua Hotel project.

16:15.550 --> 16:17.360
Mr. Huo says Mr. Mao agrees
to have his designs revised now,

16:17.360 --> 16:19.750
but who knows
if he'll change his mind later?

16:19.750 --> 16:21.910
Mr. Huo looks quite young.

16:21.910 --> 16:22.790
I'm not sure

16:22.790 --> 16:24.080
how reliable his words are.

16:24.080 --> 16:25.270
If this old man

16:25.360 --> 16:27.030
is really that eccentric,

16:27.840 --> 16:29.870
there might be a change of situation.

16:29.870 --> 16:31.480
That said, no matter what,

16:31.550 --> 16:32.960
this is a good opportunity for us.

16:32.960 --> 16:33.560
Gong Yang,

16:33.790 --> 16:35.360
spend the next few days
reviewing the designs

16:35.360 --> 16:36.510
of domestic and foreign hotels.

16:36.510 --> 16:37.270
Learn from them.

16:37.270 --> 16:37.670
Got it.

16:38.910 --> 16:40.720
Mr. Huo attempts
to gain controlling rights

16:40.720 --> 16:42.320
through a revised proposal.

16:42.360 --> 16:43.390
And we in Yuanhui

16:43.630 --> 16:44.910
can also use it

16:45.120 --> 16:46.580
to achieve bigger dreams.

16:47.080 --> 16:51.130
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

16:49.080 --> 16:51.200
That's a very dangerous move of yours.

16:51.200 --> 16:52.600
You are a lawyer.

16:52.670 --> 16:53.270
You can't always

16:53.270 --> 16:54.840
let emotions cloud your judgement!

16:54.840 --> 16:56.360
Exactly because I am a lawyer,

16:56.360 --> 16:57.600
I must thoroughly investigate this matter

16:57.600 --> 16:58.860
and uncover the truth.

16:59.150 --> 17:00.550
It was an accident,

17:00.550 --> 17:01.960
as I've told you many times.

17:01.960 --> 17:03.550
What truth are you trying to uncover?

17:03.550 --> 17:04.109
Was it so?

17:04.750 --> 17:06.069
Was it really an accident?

17:06.069 --> 17:07.000
On that very day,

17:07.349 --> 17:08.240
someone asked us to meet

17:08.240 --> 17:09.480
at the construction site to tell us

17:09.480 --> 17:10.720
a lead on the smuggling case.

17:10.720 --> 17:12.069
Was it really a coincidence

17:12.069 --> 17:14.030
that danger happened when we just arrived?

17:14.030 --> 17:15.160
That suspicious temp worker

17:15.160 --> 17:16.400
has never shown up again.

17:16.400 --> 17:17.920
It's been almost two years.

17:17.920 --> 17:19.069
Fewer and fewer of the workers

17:19.069 --> 17:20.310
from back then can be found now.

17:20.310 --> 17:21.310
Do you really think

17:21.310 --> 17:22.770
that was just an accident?

17:27.480 --> 17:28.079
Come here.

17:28.680 --> 17:30.110
Do you dare say before Shi Kai's desk

17:30.110 --> 17:32.240
that his death was purely accidental?

17:35.640 --> 17:36.200
Senior,

17:39.110 --> 17:40.790
I won't let my work be affected.

17:40.790 --> 17:41.480
But I am determined

17:41.480 --> 17:43.410
to get to the bottom of this matter.

17:43.640 --> 17:45.070
You'll head to Hangcheng
for a business trip tomorrow

17:45.070 --> 17:46.110
to go over the contract details

17:46.110 --> 17:47.040
with the client.

17:47.550 --> 17:48.070
Senior!

17:48.270 --> 17:48.720
Didn't you say

17:48.720 --> 17:49.790
you wouldn't let your work be affected?

17:49.790 --> 17:51.450
This is not up for discussion!

18:09.160 --> 18:09.690
Here come

18:09.830 --> 18:10.550
the noodles.

18:10.550 --> 18:11.080
Try some.

18:11.640 --> 18:12.100
Hang on.

18:12.350 --> 18:13.550
Let me put these away.

18:16.830 --> 18:17.310
Try it.

18:19.550 --> 18:20.410
Smells so good.

18:24.110 --> 18:24.710
Take this.

18:25.240 --> 18:26.170
It's well mixed.

18:30.310 --> 18:31.040
Give it a try.

18:34.200 --> 18:34.750
So tasty.

18:34.920 --> 18:35.580
Tasty, huh?

18:39.160 --> 18:40.360
Did you lock the door?

18:40.480 --> 18:41.400
They won't barge in later,

18:41.400 --> 18:42.110
will they?

18:44.550 --> 18:45.070
Wei said

18:45.070 --> 18:46.350
they'd do inventory tonight.

18:46.350 --> 18:47.880
So they won't be back early.

18:53.750 --> 18:54.160
We're leaving.

18:54.160 --> 18:54.720
Bye, guys.

18:54.720 --> 18:55.070
See you tomorrow.

18:55.070 --> 18:56.030
Good work today. See you tomorrow.

18:56.030 --> 18:56.550
Bye.

18:57.750 --> 18:58.270
Bai!

18:58.880 --> 18:59.310
Kang.

18:59.550 --> 19:00.080
Mr. Xiao.

19:00.590 --> 19:01.120
Mr. Xiao.

19:01.270 --> 19:02.310
I ordered from you because I have faith

19:02.310 --> 19:03.660
in the quality of your products.

19:03.660 --> 19:04.640
But the furniture I bought here

19:04.640 --> 19:05.830
warped in less than three months.

19:05.830 --> 19:06.960
What was that about?

19:07.280 --> 19:07.830
I'm so sorry.

19:07.830 --> 19:08.240
My apologies,

19:08.240 --> 19:08.770
Mr. Xiao.

19:09.000 --> 19:09.730
Don't worry.

19:09.840 --> 19:10.690
We will take

19:10.720 --> 19:11.790
full responsibility

19:11.790 --> 19:13.400
for all orders placed with us.

19:13.400 --> 19:14.400
Look,

19:14.440 --> 19:15.310
it's already nighttime.

19:15.310 --> 19:16.070
Tomorrow morning,

19:16.070 --> 19:17.000
I'll quickly go to your place

19:17.000 --> 19:17.890
to check out on the items.

19:17.890 --> 19:18.920
Then we'll discuss

19:18.920 --> 19:19.480
what to do.

19:19.480 --> 19:20.210
Is that okay?

19:21.000 --> 19:21.440
Fine.

19:21.790 --> 19:23.160
Come to my place tomorrow morning then.

19:23.160 --> 19:23.790
Sure thing.

19:23.790 --> 19:24.400
Anyway, I demand

19:24.400 --> 19:25.260
replacements.

19:25.270 --> 19:25.790
You got it.

19:25.790 --> 19:26.640
Rest assured, Mr. Xiao.

19:26.640 --> 19:27.920
Here at Happy Home Materials,

19:27.920 --> 19:29.720
we fully guarantee the quality.

19:30.070 --> 19:31.670
Alright, I'll take off then.

19:32.150 --> 19:32.590
Okay, bye.

19:32.590 --> 19:33.720
Take care, Mr. Xiao.

19:35.160 --> 19:35.890
Let me check.

19:36.640 --> 19:37.720
What happened?

19:39.200 --> 19:39.830
The ledger?

19:39.830 --> 19:40.510
This is the one.

19:40.510 --> 19:41.750
This is

19:42.030 --> 19:43.550
Mr. Xiao's order history,

19:43.960 --> 19:45.620
from the opening day till now.

19:45.640 --> 19:46.640
Let's take a look.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.110
Mr. Xiao has placed

19:48.270 --> 19:49.480
many orders with us.

19:49.550 --> 19:49.920
Yes.

19:49.920 --> 19:51.350
Hardware, bathroom fixtures, and materials

19:51.350 --> 19:52.110
like panels.

19:52.350 --> 19:54.350
Look at these two orders for panels.

19:54.350 --> 19:56.080
They were both handled by Shao.

19:56.350 --> 19:57.640
Look at these two orders.

19:57.640 --> 19:59.270
They were placed and canceled

19:59.270 --> 20:00.510
on the same day.

20:01.110 --> 20:02.570
This is indeed a bit weird.

20:02.680 --> 20:03.680
Shall we ask Xiaolan

20:03.680 --> 20:04.880
what to do about this?

20:05.110 --> 20:06.350
Ask Xiaolan?

20:06.750 --> 20:08.750
She's your friend, not your mother.

20:08.960 --> 20:09.750
We can't ask her all the time,

20:09.750 --> 20:10.440
or when will the two of us

20:10.440 --> 20:11.240
truly grow?

20:11.830 --> 20:12.240
Got it.

20:19.680 --> 20:21.310
Are you in a bad mood today?

20:23.030 --> 20:23.720
No, I'm not.

20:24.790 --> 20:26.250
I just had a little dispute

20:26.310 --> 20:27.110
with my senior

20:27.830 --> 20:28.590
on a case.

20:30.320 --> 20:31.650
You don't usually

20:31.680 --> 20:32.680
bring home

20:32.680 --> 20:34.140
the negativity from work.

20:35.240 --> 20:36.970
You mean Shi Kai's case, right?

20:41.750 --> 20:43.280
It's been nearly two years.

20:43.440 --> 20:44.310
But there hasn't been a lead

20:44.310 --> 20:45.440
on that temp worker.

20:46.590 --> 20:47.550
My senior keeps trying to convince me

20:47.550 --> 20:49.080
that it was just an accident

20:49.400 --> 20:51.460
and stopping me from probing deeper.

20:51.480 --> 20:53.000
I planned to visit the construction crew

20:53.000 --> 20:54.460
tomorrow, yet he insisted

20:54.510 --> 20:56.510
I go to Hangcheng on a business trip.

20:56.960 --> 20:58.400
In fact, that Hangcheng contract

20:58.400 --> 20:59.680
has been going very smoothly.

20:59.680 --> 21:01.480
There's no need for a trip at all.

21:02.790 --> 21:05.270
Hangcheng is a lovely place.

21:08.720 --> 21:09.380
Zhou Cheng,

21:10.030 --> 21:11.640
now that you're in a bad mood,

21:11.920 --> 21:13.640
how about I accompany you to Hangcheng

21:13.640 --> 21:15.030
where we can relax a bit?

21:17.880 --> 21:20.070
Are you trying to keep me company,

21:20.440 --> 21:21.400
or...

21:23.030 --> 21:23.880
Fine.

21:24.480 --> 21:25.270
To be frank,

21:25.270 --> 21:27.800
I'm going to visit
an eccentric old man there.

21:28.180 --> 21:29.510
What eccentric old man?

21:30.680 --> 21:32.340
You'll know when we get there.

21:35.430 --> 21:39.650
[Hangcheng]
[No. 1 Architectural Design  Institute]

21:36.960 --> 21:37.510
Hello.

21:37.750 --> 21:39.610
I'm here to meet Mr. Mao Kangshan.

21:39.750 --> 21:40.950
Mr. Mao isn't around.

21:41.070 --> 21:42.480
He never meets anyone

21:42.510 --> 21:43.550
without an appointment.

21:43.550 --> 21:44.400
I'll make one then.

21:44.400 --> 21:45.800
May I ask where to do that?

21:45.880 --> 21:46.740
Appointments?

21:47.270 --> 21:49.130
We don't offer that service here.

21:50.000 --> 21:51.310
No meetings without an appointment

21:51.310 --> 21:52.790
and no way to make an appointment.

21:52.790 --> 21:55.320
Mr. Mao is clearly
not giving anyone a chance.

21:55.400 --> 21:56.270
You're right.

21:56.590 --> 21:58.030
He just hates to meet people like you

21:58.030 --> 21:59.240
who harbor ulterior motives.

21:59.240 --> 21:59.720
Leave.

21:59.920 --> 22:01.180
Don't come here again.

22:04.070 --> 22:05.070
I'll have one more talk

22:05.070 --> 22:06.240
with Yaxing Foreign Trading

22:06.240 --> 22:07.550
to flesh out the contract soon.

22:07.550 --> 22:07.960
Okay.

22:08.200 --> 22:09.330
Thank you, Mr. Zhou,

22:09.550 --> 22:10.960
for making a trip.

22:11.160 --> 22:12.110
No problem. It's my job.

22:12.110 --> 22:12.910
Thanks again.

22:18.550 --> 22:18.960
This is

22:19.000 --> 22:20.590
a work by a master architect in Hangcheng,

22:20.590 --> 22:22.050
who is named Mao Kangshan.

22:22.400 --> 22:23.600
It's a real treasure.

22:26.350 --> 22:27.610
I heard Mr. Mao's works

22:28.070 --> 22:29.720
are rarely found on the market.

22:29.720 --> 22:30.120
Right.

22:30.510 --> 22:30.970
This was

22:31.000 --> 22:32.640
created by him when he was young.

22:32.640 --> 22:33.350
My family has been

22:33.350 --> 22:34.960
friends with Mr. Mao's for generations,

22:34.960 --> 22:36.890
so I've known him since childhood.

22:53.640 --> 22:56.500
I can remember fewer and fewer things
from the past.

22:56.720 --> 22:58.250
Will there be a day when I...

23:00.960 --> 23:01.640
Come in!

23:10.590 --> 23:11.520
Anything wrong?

23:11.650 --> 23:12.580
You had a bad day?

23:12.680 --> 23:14.350
The institute wouldn't let me in.

23:14.350 --> 23:15.720
I plan to try my luck
at the family quarters

23:15.720 --> 23:16.400
tomorrow.

23:17.400 --> 23:19.330
I know it's not a proper thing to do,

23:19.350 --> 23:20.510
yet I just can't quit

23:20.510 --> 23:21.840
before meeting Mr. Mao.

23:22.110 --> 23:23.640
I heard that he would chase away

23:23.640 --> 23:24.790
all visitors to his place.

23:24.790 --> 23:26.200
I'm not sure if I'll be able

23:26.200 --> 23:28.200
to get him to open the door tomorrow.

23:29.240 --> 23:30.370
I have a piece of news

23:30.830 --> 23:31.790
about Mr. Mao.

23:32.150 --> 23:32.830
Tell me now.

23:46.210 --> 23:47.470
Trimming vegetables?

23:47.510 --> 23:48.240
Yes.

23:49.350 --> 23:51.550
I'm going to dry these on this sunny day.

23:51.720 --> 23:52.350
Hello.

23:52.920 --> 23:53.510
May I ask

23:53.510 --> 23:54.350
if Mr. Mao Kangshan

23:54.350 --> 23:55.200
lives here?

23:55.550 --> 23:56.110
Yes.

23:56.440 --> 23:58.000
Why are you looking for him?

23:58.830 --> 23:59.430
Well, I...

24:00.310 --> 24:00.970
Zhou Cheng!

24:01.200 --> 24:02.530
Is it heavy? Let me help.

24:02.720 --> 24:03.210
Not at all.

24:03.210 --> 24:03.720
It's confirmed

24:03.720 --> 24:05.050
that Mr. Mao lives here.

24:06.160 --> 24:06.750
Yes, he does.

24:06.750 --> 24:07.590
Mr. Mao Kangshan

24:07.590 --> 24:08.990
lives on the sixth floor.

24:09.350 --> 24:10.070
We'd hate to bother you...

24:10.070 --> 24:10.720
I'm going upstairs anyway.

24:10.720 --> 24:11.790
Let me take you to his place.

24:11.790 --> 24:12.240
Thank you.

24:12.240 --> 24:12.770
Let's go.

24:20.510 --> 24:22.720
What was the provincial institute
thinking?

24:22.720 --> 24:23.920
Did they not consider

24:24.160 --> 24:25.000
Mr. Mao's age at all

24:25.000 --> 24:26.260
when they assigned him

24:26.440 --> 24:27.900
a sixth-floor apartment?

24:28.270 --> 24:30.270
I can imagine how inconvenient for him

24:30.270 --> 24:31.600
to go out for groceries.

24:31.750 --> 24:33.010
This is his apartment.

24:33.200 --> 24:34.860
Knock on the door yourselves.

24:36.720 --> 24:37.520
Zheng Shuqin!

24:38.510 --> 24:40.910
You're Mr. Mao's daughter-in-law, right?

24:41.310 --> 24:42.160
I know Mr. Mao

24:42.160 --> 24:44.030
is reluctant to meet with strangers.

24:44.030 --> 24:45.750
Can you knock on his door for me?

24:45.750 --> 24:47.410
Y-Y-You're asking me to do it?

24:49.440 --> 24:50.920
How did you know who I am?

24:52.110 --> 24:52.880
Your story is well-known

24:52.880 --> 24:55.200
at the povincial architectural institute.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.270
I heard that they originally

24:56.270 --> 24:57.400
assigned Mr. Mao

24:57.400 --> 24:59.510
a large apartment on the third floor,

24:59.640 --> 25:00.750
and his son, Mao Guosheng,

25:00.750 --> 25:02.410
a small one on the sixth floor.

25:02.610 --> 25:03.400
But surprisingly,

25:03.400 --> 25:04.720
you took the apartment on the third floor

25:04.720 --> 25:06.920
and made Mr. Mao live on the sixth floor.

25:06.960 --> 25:07.830
Hey, young lady,

25:07.830 --> 25:09.160
what's all that nonsense from?

25:09.160 --> 25:10.510
Mr. Mao voluntarily let us

25:10.510 --> 25:11.550
take his apartment.

25:11.550 --> 25:12.200
Really?

25:12.680 --> 25:13.680
But you didn't say

25:13.680 --> 25:14.680
the exact reason.

25:14.720 --> 25:15.550
Mr. Mao did it for the good

25:15.550 --> 25:16.640
of his grandson, didn't he?

25:16.640 --> 25:18.560
Who would've known
you'd have the nerve to ask for it?

25:18.560 --> 25:19.240
If I were you,

25:19.240 --> 25:20.830
I couldn't have been so thick-skinned.

25:20.830 --> 25:22.070
Who are you calling thick-skinned?

25:22.070 --> 25:23.160
Stop arguing at my door.

25:23.160 --> 25:23.880
This is annoying.

25:23.880 --> 25:24.510
Go away!

25:25.160 --> 25:25.920
Mr. Mao.

25:27.000 --> 25:27.480
What?

25:28.110 --> 25:29.680
Are you forcing your way into my home?

25:29.680 --> 25:31.350
We're terribly sorry, Mr. Mao.

25:31.350 --> 25:32.550
We had no choice

25:32.790 --> 25:33.880
but to show up at your door

25:33.880 --> 25:34.680
so abruptly.

25:35.160 --> 25:35.920
Mr. Mao,

25:36.240 --> 25:37.510
we are here for the Haihua Hotel

25:37.510 --> 25:38.400
project.

25:38.640 --> 25:39.970
All I need is 10 minutes.

25:40.790 --> 25:41.850
What are these for?

25:43.400 --> 25:44.200
Well, you see,

25:44.550 --> 25:45.400
this is my first visit.

25:45.400 --> 25:46.640
I can't show up empty-handed, right?

25:46.640 --> 25:48.200
I'd like you to take these gifts
and be my tutor.

25:48.200 --> 25:50.260
Did anyone say I'd take apprentices?

25:50.270 --> 25:51.400
D-Do I even know you?

25:51.790 --> 25:53.450
Let me introduce myself then.

25:54.070 --> 25:54.930
Hello, Mr. Mao.

25:55.030 --> 25:56.290
My name is Xia Xiaolan.

25:56.350 --> 25:57.880
I do renovation work in Shengcheng.

25:57.880 --> 25:58.920
The company I'm in will take part

25:58.920 --> 26:00.520
in the Haihua Hotel project.

26:00.920 --> 26:01.590
I've agreed

26:01.590 --> 26:03.070
to have my designs modified.

26:03.070 --> 26:04.070
You may leave now.

26:04.480 --> 26:05.350
Mr. Mao.

26:06.270 --> 26:07.200
Everyone outside says

26:07.200 --> 26:08.660
you have a strange temper.

26:08.720 --> 26:09.750
But to my knowledge,

26:09.750 --> 26:11.070
you not only possess great talent,

26:11.070 --> 26:12.330
but great virtues too.

26:12.510 --> 26:13.270
The renovation of Haihua Hotel

26:13.270 --> 26:14.670
is a commercial project.

26:14.750 --> 26:16.110
Out of respect for the contract

26:16.110 --> 26:17.310
and your work partners,

26:17.310 --> 26:18.920
you agreed to have the designs modified,

26:18.920 --> 26:20.240
even though you knew

26:20.400 --> 26:21.800
there was nothing wrong.

26:23.960 --> 26:25.160
So, today, I'm here

26:25.310 --> 26:26.790
not only to talk to you

26:26.790 --> 26:27.920
about Haihua Hotel.

26:28.510 --> 26:29.480
Shengcheng

26:29.480 --> 26:31.140
is a rapidly developing city.

26:31.240 --> 26:32.910
Every day, there are new buildings,

26:32.910 --> 26:33.880
new opportunities,

26:33.880 --> 26:34.790
and new dreams.

26:37.000 --> 26:39.200
I'd like to talk to you about the future.

26:45.720 --> 26:46.180
Hurry.

26:52.350 --> 26:53.830
It's been a long time
since someone had the guts

26:53.830 --> 26:55.070
to bring gifts to your father-in-law.

26:55.070 --> 26:57.110
Aren't they afraid of being kicked out?

26:57.110 --> 26:58.200
This is really odd.

26:58.750 --> 27:00.680
What a shock they're still in there.

27:00.680 --> 27:02.280
What are they talking about?

27:14.160 --> 27:16.220
Tell me about your idea of the future.

27:24.870 --> 27:26.280
[Qihang Architectural Design Firm
Retainer Agreement]

27:32.720 --> 27:33.960
You're planning to start

27:33.960 --> 27:35.620
your own architectural firm?

27:35.720 --> 27:36.240
Yes.

27:37.210 --> 27:37.840
Mr. Mao,

27:38.440 --> 27:40.240
I know you are not only talented,

27:40.520 --> 27:41.830
but also aspired to cultivate

27:41.830 --> 27:42.550
the next generation

27:42.550 --> 27:44.000
of architects for the industry.

27:44.000 --> 27:45.400
So, this time, I came here

27:45.460 --> 27:47.160
with the hope of you serving as the pillar

27:47.160 --> 27:49.420
of my architectural firm in Shengcheng.

27:49.720 --> 27:51.110
I hope that one day,

27:51.440 --> 27:52.240
my firm can grow

27:52.240 --> 27:53.640
to be like the foreign ones

27:53.640 --> 27:55.960
and become a dream place
and a starting point

27:55.960 --> 27:57.310
for all architects.

27:59.830 --> 28:00.640
Do you know...

28:01.510 --> 28:03.910
what ambitious remarks you're saying now?

28:04.880 --> 28:05.540
Yes, I know.

28:06.270 --> 28:07.920
I graduated only two years ago.

28:07.920 --> 28:09.200
It's fair to say I haven't really

28:09.200 --> 28:10.000
crossed the threshold

28:10.000 --> 28:11.000
of this industry.

28:11.200 --> 28:13.720
Yet here I am,
saying something like a fantasy.

28:13.720 --> 28:15.050
The old me wouldn't have

28:15.110 --> 28:16.640
dared make a dream this big.

28:17.070 --> 28:17.640
But if

28:17.640 --> 28:18.680
we don't aim high,

28:19.000 --> 28:19.880
how do we know

28:19.920 --> 28:21.110
if we're able to make our dreams

28:21.110 --> 28:21.790
come true?

28:25.160 --> 28:26.200
There are ice pops in the fridge.

28:26.200 --> 28:27.110
Help yourself.

28:27.350 --> 28:28.210
Thanks, but no.

28:28.590 --> 28:29.650
Would you like one?

28:31.400 --> 28:32.150
Mr. Mao,

28:33.110 --> 28:34.710
I believe you aren't content

28:34.920 --> 28:35.590
to just be

28:35.590 --> 28:37.190
a reclusive master, are you?

28:44.160 --> 28:44.960
I've got you

28:45.030 --> 28:46.590
all the panel samples

28:46.590 --> 28:47.680
you picked last time.

28:47.680 --> 28:48.010
Okay.

28:48.750 --> 28:49.480
Hey, Shao,

28:49.680 --> 28:50.940
-come over.
-Mr. Kang.

28:51.030 --> 28:51.960
Give Ms. Wei here

28:52.000 --> 28:53.350
a detailed introduction

28:53.350 --> 28:54.400
on our panels.

28:54.440 --> 28:55.070
Sure, Mr. Kang.

28:55.070 --> 28:55.400
Please.

28:55.400 --> 28:55.750
Okay.

28:55.830 --> 28:56.480
Ms. Wei, please.

28:56.480 --> 28:56.810
Okay.

28:57.550 --> 28:58.110
Ms. Wei, look.

28:58.110 --> 28:59.440
These three types of panels

28:59.440 --> 29:00.750
are what you chose last time.

29:00.750 --> 29:01.110
Yes.

29:01.110 --> 29:01.920
They come in

29:01.920 --> 29:02.920
different sizes,

29:03.550 --> 29:05.000
materials,

29:05.000 --> 29:06.160
and various

29:06.160 --> 29:06.880
colors.

29:07.400 --> 29:08.030
If you're going for

29:08.030 --> 29:09.030
a simple, minimalist style

29:09.030 --> 29:10.510
for your home improvement project,

29:10.510 --> 29:11.480
I think this color

29:11.480 --> 29:12.740
could be a good choice.

29:13.070 --> 29:16.940
[Affordable and high-quality products
at Happy Home Materials]

29:13.330 --> 29:14.640
Shall we grab a bite after work?

29:14.640 --> 29:15.200
Okay.

29:15.480 --> 29:16.740
Bye, Ms. Bai, Mr. Kang.

29:17.070 --> 29:17.720
See you tomorrow.

29:17.720 --> 29:18.270
Good work today.

29:18.270 --> 29:19.270
See you tomorrow.

29:19.310 --> 29:20.510
See you tomorrow, Ms. Bai, Mr. Kang.

29:20.510 --> 29:22.110
Good work. See you tomorrow.

29:29.680 --> 29:30.440
I'll follow them.

29:30.440 --> 29:31.550
Come after you lock up the doors.

29:31.550 --> 29:32.240
Be careful.

29:49.480 --> 29:50.940
So this is a panel factory.

29:51.720 --> 29:53.250
Shao really is the culprit.

30:03.030 --> 30:04.640
T-They've outnumbered us.

30:05.550 --> 30:06.150
Sis Bai...

30:07.440 --> 30:08.000
Sis Bai?

30:10.550 --> 30:10.880
Yes.

30:11.270 --> 30:11.800
Come now.

30:17.350 --> 30:18.030
You scared me.

30:18.030 --> 30:18.830
What were you doing?

30:18.830 --> 30:19.920
Calling for backup.

30:19.920 --> 30:20.680
Smart move.

30:21.440 --> 30:22.570
I've figured it out.

30:22.680 --> 30:23.750
Shao faked those

30:23.750 --> 30:24.880
canceled order records,

30:24.880 --> 30:25.480
and had this factory

30:25.480 --> 30:26.960
make the products in secret.

30:26.960 --> 30:27.590
He then sent

30:27.590 --> 30:28.550
the shoddy goods to the client

30:28.550 --> 30:30.550
in the name of Happy Home Materials.

30:32.750 --> 30:34.010
What are you two doing?

30:34.070 --> 30:35.110
You seem sneaky.

30:35.160 --> 30:35.760
Come over!

30:36.480 --> 30:37.270
-Where’s the backup?
-Come here now!

30:37.270 --> 30:38.070
Not here yet.

30:38.070 --> 30:40.470
Who would've known
we'd get caught so soon?

30:40.960 --> 30:43.160
You're director of the factory, right?

30:43.680 --> 30:45.680
Well, I'd like to place an order.

30:46.000 --> 30:47.030
But we need a massive number

30:47.030 --> 30:47.760
of products.

30:47.960 --> 30:48.510
I wonder

30:48.510 --> 30:50.170
if your factory can handle it.

30:50.880 --> 30:51.740
Place an order?

30:52.680 --> 30:53.310
For what?

30:53.920 --> 30:54.440
Isn't your factory...

30:54.440 --> 30:54.920
Uncle!

30:56.110 --> 30:56.840
Those two...

30:57.000 --> 30:57.920
are Mr. Kang and Mr. Bai

30:57.920 --> 30:59.510
from the Happy Home Materials!

30:59.510 --> 31:00.920
What? You're such

31:00.920 --> 31:01.580
an ingrate.

31:03.030 --> 31:04.890
Now that you've recognized Shao,

31:05.350 --> 31:07.480
I have one more reason not to let you go.

31:07.750 --> 31:08.610
Take them down!

31:11.640 --> 31:13.100
Stop, or you'll regret it!

31:15.200 --> 31:16.440
Only San is here to back us up?

31:16.440 --> 31:17.840
He's all the help we need.

31:22.960 --> 31:24.160
If you dare to attack,

31:24.310 --> 31:25.910
I'll fight in self-defense!

31:28.920 --> 31:29.350
Wait.

31:29.960 --> 31:30.720
Who are you?

31:31.400 --> 31:32.800
What are you waiting for?

31:33.240 --> 31:33.960
Go get him!

31:48.570 --> 31:49.430
Quick, hit him!

31:49.750 --> 31:50.410
Beat him up!

31:51.480 --> 31:52.070
Go get...

32:19.030 --> 32:19.490
Hit him!

32:45.550 --> 32:46.550
Here we are! Here!

32:47.200 --> 32:48.480
-Freeze!
-Nobody move!

32:48.480 --> 32:49.210
Arrest them!

32:51.400 --> 32:51.830
Get up!

32:52.880 --> 32:53.920
You, get up!

32:55.310 --> 32:56.570
-Don't move!
-Behave!

32:56.750 --> 32:57.350
Cuff them!

33:00.030 --> 33:01.160
You're fired.

33:03.880 --> 33:05.680
A lawyer's letter will find you.

33:09.200 --> 33:11.800
I told you not to make me fight
in self-defense.

33:12.270 --> 33:12.640
Go!

33:13.880 --> 33:14.810
Behave, you lot!

33:15.720 --> 33:16.160
Go!

33:19.590 --> 33:20.120
Let's go.

33:36.030 --> 33:36.560
What now?

33:36.830 --> 33:38.090
Have you warmed up yet?

33:38.240 --> 33:39.240
Let's test it out.

33:39.680 --> 33:40.210
Off we go!

33:43.070 --> 33:43.640
Wei,

33:43.910 --> 33:44.680
go home yourself.

33:44.680 --> 33:46.350
I'm heading to the boxing gym with San.

33:46.350 --> 33:47.180
Okay, got it.

33:56.590 --> 33:57.590
The two of them...

33:57.680 --> 33:59.280
have such strong physiques.

34:00.160 --> 34:00.790
Not bad.

34:01.120 --> 34:01.850
The two of you

34:01.860 --> 34:03.460
can fend for yourselves now.

34:03.550 --> 34:04.080
Alright.

34:04.270 --> 34:05.670
We'll talk when I'm back.

34:06.240 --> 34:06.640
Bye.

34:08.190 --> 34:09.190
Was that Zhenzhu?

34:09.360 --> 34:09.760
Yes.

34:10.840 --> 34:12.320
Shao, an employee of the materials store,

34:12.320 --> 34:13.230
colluded with a relative of his

34:13.230 --> 34:14.280
to pass off shoddy goods as quality ones.

34:14.280 --> 34:15.940
Sis Bai and Wei took them down.

34:16.400 --> 34:17.030
Wei already bragged to me

34:17.030 --> 34:18.400
about it for quite a while.

34:18.400 --> 34:19.070
Shall we hang out

34:19.070 --> 34:20.230
in Hangcheng in the next two days?

34:20.230 --> 34:21.030
We can go back to Shengcheng

34:21.030 --> 34:22.820
with Mr. Mao when he agrees to join us.

34:22.820 --> 34:24.820
But he hasn't nodded yet.

34:24.880 --> 34:26.000
What gives you that confidence?

34:26.000 --> 34:27.659
I just have confidence in you.

34:31.070 --> 34:31.440
Look.

34:31.750 --> 34:33.000
Isn't it pretty over there?

34:33.000 --> 34:33.460
This...

34:33.670 --> 34:34.870
is really beautiful.

34:36.030 --> 34:37.889
Look at that Dingsheng cake shop.

34:37.960 --> 34:39.150
What a queue of people.

34:39.150 --> 34:40.150
It's auspicuous,

34:40.280 --> 34:41.440
since this cake symbolizes victory.

34:41.440 --> 34:42.440
Why don't we buy some?

34:42.440 --> 34:42.800
Sure.

34:43.190 --> 34:44.320
I'll go check it out.

34:52.550 --> 34:53.190
Xiaolan?

34:59.150 --> 34:59.880
Xiaolan?

35:05.670 --> 35:06.400
Xiaolan?

35:10.400 --> 35:12.230
Gosh. You gave me such a fright!

35:12.920 --> 35:14.320
Come on, have some water.

35:15.000 --> 35:15.530
Xiaolan,

35:15.960 --> 35:16.710
is it fun in Hangcheng?

35:16.710 --> 35:17.910
Slow down. Easy on it.

35:18.110 --> 35:18.710
Yes.

35:18.760 --> 35:19.290
Fun, huh?

35:19.590 --> 35:20.520
Then from now on,

35:20.840 --> 35:21.590
let's have

35:21.590 --> 35:22.990
a family trip every year.

35:24.320 --> 35:25.120
Hangcheng...

35:25.920 --> 35:27.000
I visited Hangcheng with Mom and Dad
years ago.

35:27.000 --> 35:28.930
Xiaolan, you must be tired, right?

35:29.070 --> 35:29.530
Come on.

35:30.280 --> 35:31.400
I'll carry you on my back.

35:31.400 --> 35:31.930
Careful.

35:56.900 --> 35:58.480
[Hoxter Clocks and Watches]

36:00.510 --> 36:01.510
Come in for a look.

36:07.480 --> 36:08.480
Pick one you like.

36:18.000 --> 36:18.800
You like this?

36:19.110 --> 36:20.670
You do have a good eye, miss.

36:21.030 --> 36:22.290
It's an imported good.

36:22.320 --> 36:23.180
You can't buy it

36:23.230 --> 36:24.090
anywhere else.

36:26.510 --> 36:26.960
One.

36:27.670 --> 36:28.110
Two.

36:28.920 --> 36:29.320
Three.

36:32.510 --> 36:33.550
It's so pretty!

36:34.030 --> 36:34.560
Isn't it?

36:34.710 --> 36:35.320
Yes, it is.

36:38.230 --> 36:39.290
Alright, careful!

36:46.190 --> 36:46.850
You like it?

36:47.110 --> 36:48.310
If you do, buy it then.

36:49.030 --> 36:50.650
You seem to really like alarm clocks.

36:50.650 --> 36:51.630
You were buying an alarm clock

36:51.630 --> 36:52.760
when I first met you.

36:52.920 --> 36:53.780
I won't take it.

36:53.810 --> 36:54.740
Thanks, though.

36:56.280 --> 36:57.140
Why not buy one?

37:10.160 --> 37:11.190
How is it? Beautiful, right?

37:11.190 --> 37:11.590
Yes.

37:13.550 --> 37:15.110
Which is prettier, me or the scenery?

37:15.110 --> 37:15.550
You.

37:19.710 --> 37:21.480
There used to stand the Leifeng Pagoda,
right?

37:21.480 --> 37:21.880
Right.

37:22.630 --> 37:24.190
It's a pity that it collapsed long ago.

37:24.190 --> 37:25.850
Luckily, the story survived.

37:27.440 --> 37:28.630
Bai Suzhen the snake spirit

37:28.630 --> 37:29.230
and Xu Xian were

37:29.230 --> 37:30.760
from different worlds to begin with.

37:30.760 --> 37:31.710
Despite the huge difference,

37:31.710 --> 37:33.710
they fell for each other
against heaven's will.

37:33.710 --> 37:35.310
Bai Suzhen paid a steep price

37:35.480 --> 37:38.070
by being trapped in the Leifeng Pagoda
for 18 years.

37:38.070 --> 37:38.930
Was it worth it?

37:39.670 --> 37:40.800
Sometimes, it is

37:41.360 --> 37:42.480
through hardships

37:42.480 --> 37:44.210
that love shows its true worth.

37:44.710 --> 37:46.310
But I don't need to go through

37:46.800 --> 37:48.000
hardships to realize

37:48.480 --> 37:51.080
that you're the most precious of all
in my life.

37:56.190 --> 37:56.720
Xiaolan,

37:58.630 --> 37:59.690
let's get married.

38:02.710 --> 38:03.710
Didn't we agree

38:04.360 --> 38:05.800
to register for marriage

38:06.070 --> 38:07.400
when Luna had 50 stores?

38:07.710 --> 38:09.640
It should be about time now, right?

38:10.590 --> 38:11.250
Zhou Cheng,

38:11.960 --> 38:12.880
when I completely

38:12.880 --> 38:14.610
hand over Luna to Chen Xiliang,

38:15.070 --> 38:16.000
let's register for marriage.

38:15.600 --> 38:21.560
♪ Watching the flowers fall,
lonely I ask the night sky ♪

38:17.590 --> 38:18.120
Shall we?

38:19.320 --> 38:20.590
I can't believe

38:20.840 --> 38:21.900
I nearly forgot it.

38:22.220 --> 38:27.440
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

38:23.480 --> 38:23.840
Sure.

38:24.320 --> 38:25.380
Let's get married.

38:26.440 --> 38:26.840
Great.

38:29.100 --> 38:32.050
♪ Time is so stingy ♪

38:32.070 --> 38:35.420
♪ It takes away even the memories ♪

38:36.310 --> 38:38.920
♪ But I still remember ♪

38:38.880 --> 38:39.320
Xiaolan,

38:39.110 --> 38:43.390
♪ The promises of love ♪

38:40.710 --> 38:42.570
are you worried about something?

38:43.590 --> 38:46.050
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

38:46.070 --> 38:50.780
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

38:50.810 --> 38:53.370
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

38:53.390 --> 38:57.940
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

38:58.420 --> 39:02.190
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

39:02.210 --> 39:06.420
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

39:02.510 --> 39:04.030
From forgetting who I was

39:05.110 --> 39:06.710
to forgetting who I am now...

39:07.320 --> 39:11.890
♪ We will finally reunite ♪

39:07.760 --> 39:08.510
Xia Xiaolan,

39:09.960 --> 39:10.880
Where are you?

39:12.280 --> 39:13.150
And where am I?

39:22.190 --> 39:23.800
Dear passengers,

39:24.480 --> 39:26.320
the flight from Hangcheng...

39:26.320 --> 39:27.360
We can still board the plane
if we get in there

39:27.360 --> 39:28.420
within 10 minutes.

39:28.590 --> 39:30.250
Do you think Mr. Mao will come?

39:31.030 --> 39:32.160
He definitely will.

39:32.430 --> 39:33.670
Mr. Mao is full of

39:33.670 --> 39:34.960
ideals and ambitions.

39:35.630 --> 39:37.030
If he really didn't care,

39:37.070 --> 39:38.920
he wouldn't have taken on
the Haihua Hotel project.

39:38.920 --> 39:40.000
Didn't you come to Hangcheng

39:40.000 --> 39:41.200
for this very reason?

39:42.000 --> 39:43.190
You do know me well.

39:43.630 --> 39:45.960
But he still hasn't shown up
at this point.

39:45.960 --> 39:48.090
Do you think he's stalling on purpose,

39:49.630 --> 39:50.440
or...

39:53.280 --> 39:53.880
Oh, right.

39:54.230 --> 39:55.070
Mr. Mao hasn't made a trip

39:55.070 --> 39:56.190
out of Hangcheng for so long.

39:56.190 --> 39:57.150
Could he be...

40:01.630 --> 40:02.360
Mr. Mao!

40:03.030 --> 40:03.820
Let me carry it.

40:03.820 --> 40:04.280
I...

40:04.760 --> 40:05.360
It's okay.

40:05.360 --> 40:05.760
Let me get it.

40:05.760 --> 40:07.280
Why so many procedures

40:07.280 --> 40:08.480
on the way to the airport?

40:08.480 --> 40:09.280
What a hassle.

40:09.960 --> 40:11.440
I should've been more considerate

40:11.440 --> 40:12.970
and picked you up from home.

40:13.390 --> 40:14.980
Dear passengers,

40:15.710 --> 40:17.510
the flight from Hangcheng

40:17.510 --> 40:18.590
to Shengcheng...

40:18.670 --> 40:19.510
Let's go then.

40:19.830 --> 40:20.360
Let's go.

40:20.400 --> 40:21.840
I'll just go take a look.

40:22.280 --> 40:23.030
Yes, sure.

40:23.230 --> 40:23.890
Just a look.

40:24.000 --> 40:25.480
Please take your personal belongings.

40:25.480 --> 40:26.070
That is

40:26.280 --> 40:27.110
all we need.

40:29.540 --> 40:33.590
[Shengcheng]

40:35.760 --> 40:36.890
We should've driven

40:37.150 --> 40:39.070
Zhou Cheng to the law firm
from the airport.

40:39.070 --> 40:40.590
It wouldn't have been much of a detour.

40:40.590 --> 40:41.320
Mr. Mao

40:41.320 --> 40:42.510
must be tired

40:42.530 --> 40:43.550
after that three-hour flight.

40:43.550 --> 40:45.710
It's better to go straight to the hotel.

40:45.710 --> 40:47.360
After this road was completed,

40:47.360 --> 40:48.760
it's much faster to go from the airport

40:48.760 --> 40:49.630
to downtown.

40:50.440 --> 40:50.840
Yes.

40:51.400 --> 40:52.630
Shengcheng develops quickly.

40:52.630 --> 40:53.630
It only took six months

40:53.630 --> 40:54.630
for this road to be made

40:54.630 --> 40:56.490
and many buildings to take shape.

41:14.630 --> 41:18.000
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

41:18.020 --> 41:21.460
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

41:21.640 --> 41:24.550
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

41:25.020 --> 41:28.180
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

41:28.400 --> 41:34.070
♪ That'd be enough ♪

41:33.590 --> 41:33.960
Thank you.

41:33.960 --> 41:34.550
Mr. Mao,

41:34.630 --> 41:35.960
how do you like it here?

41:36.150 --> 41:36.880
Pretty nice.

41:38.000 --> 41:38.460
Ms. Xia,

41:38.760 --> 41:39.360
it's done.

41:40.280 --> 41:40.880
Mr. Mao,

41:40.880 --> 41:42.010
get some rest today.

41:42.110 --> 41:43.840
I'll show you around tomorrow.

41:44.280 --> 41:45.410
I don't want to wait.

41:45.800 --> 41:46.760
I'd like to visit your company

41:46.760 --> 41:48.490
after dropping off my luggage.

41:49.590 --> 41:50.030
Okay.

41:52.960 --> 41:53.920
I'm back!

41:55.280 --> 41:55.780
Cheng!

41:56.760 --> 41:58.760
A Hangcheng specialty, Dingsheng cake.

41:58.760 --> 41:59.110
Chen,

41:59.210 --> 42:00.110
split it with everyone.

42:00.110 --> 42:01.170
Thanks. Good work.

42:02.440 --> 42:02.900
Come on.

42:03.110 --> 42:03.910
Time to share.

42:04.630 --> 42:05.000
Dong.

42:05.440 --> 42:06.040
Thank you.

42:06.070 --> 42:07.590
How is Hao's mood today?

42:07.630 --> 42:08.630
Hao won a case.

42:08.840 --> 42:09.440
He said

42:09.440 --> 42:11.360
he'd treat us all to a meal
some other day.

42:11.360 --> 42:12.880
If you have a favor to ask him for,
do it now.

42:12.880 --> 42:14.010
He'll surely say yes.

42:14.010 --> 42:14.970
Okay, got it.

42:15.000 --> 42:15.590
Alright.

42:15.840 --> 42:16.700
I'll have this.

42:18.440 --> 42:18.900
Thanks.

42:18.920 --> 42:19.550
Nice.

42:19.630 --> 42:20.230
It's good.

42:22.030 --> 42:22.490
Come in!

42:23.190 --> 42:23.650
Senior.

42:25.960 --> 42:27.280
Here's a Hangcheng specialty,

42:27.280 --> 42:28.210
Dingsheng cake.

42:29.590 --> 42:31.120
You came for a talk, knowing

42:31.150 --> 42:32.150
I'm in a good mood?

42:33.360 --> 42:34.220
Check this out.

42:36.320 --> 42:36.920
What is it?

42:37.550 --> 42:38.280
Just read it.

42:43.400 --> 42:44.350
[Investigation Report]
[The missing worker, Wang Qiang]

42:44.960 --> 42:46.070
He's that missing worker?
